    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can the ERP work offline at remote sites?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. We build offline-first modules for warehouses, factories, and field locations with poor connectivity. Data syncs to the central server when the network is back, with conflict resolution rules.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

`} />
</BaseLayout>
